<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <title>Hotel Management Software</title>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="w-screen h-screen flex">
        <form action="/user/register" method="post" class="h-full w-1/2 bg-slate-800 p-10 rounded-sm bg-sla-500 flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="pb-12 text-4xl text-white font-bold">
                <h1>Register your Account</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-2">
                <label for="username" class="text-white text-lg">Enter username: </label> <br>
                <input type="text" name="username" id="username" placeholder="Enter username" required autocomplete="off" class="w-80  h-8 p-1  rounded-md  focus:outline-none">
            </div>
            <div class="mt-2">
                <label for="username" class="text-white text-lg">Enter Full Name: </label> <br>
                <input type="text" name="fullName" id="username" placeholder="Enter username" required autocomplete="off" class="w-80  h-8 p-1  rounded-md  focus:outline-none">
            </div>
            <div class="mt-2">
                <label for="email" class="text-white text-lg">Enter your Email</label> <br>
                <input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="Enter your Email" required autocomplete="off" class="w-80  h-8 p-1  rounded-md  focus:outline-none">
            </div>
            <div class="mt-2">
                <label for="age" class="text-white text-lg">Enter your Age:</label> <br>
                <input type="number" name="age" id="age" placeholder="Enter your age" required autocomplete="off" class="w-80  h-8 p-1  rounded-md  focus:outline-none">
            </div>
            <div class="mt-2 mb-2">
                <label for="password" class="text-white text-lg">Enter your password</label> <br>
                <input type="password" name="password" id="password" placeholder="Enter your password" required autocomplete="off" class="w-80  h-8 p-1  rounded-md  focus:outline-none"> <br>
                <a href="/login" class="text-xs text-orange-600 underline">Already have an account</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <button type="submit" class="w-20 h-10 bg-sky-500 rounded-md mt-3">Submit</button>
            </div>
        </form>

        <section class="w-1/2 h-full p-5 pt-20 bg-black">
            <div class="text-white">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold">Hello,</h1>
                <p class="w-3/4 pb-4">
                    Here you can create your account and login and manage your hotel as your wish
                    Just create an account and start your hotel. You can know your rooms data and
                    and also you have the capability of adding room in dashboard.
                </p>
                <h3 class="text-6xl font-semibold mt-9">Thankyou!</h3>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>